Interface MASGroupIdentity

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    MASGroupRepository
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MASGroup

    public interface MASGroupIdentity
    This interface enables Identity Management features for the MASGroup object.

void getAllGroups(java.lang.String owner,
                              MASCallback<java.util.List<MASGroup>> callback)
        Deprecated. Please use getGroupsByFilter(MASFilteredRequest, MASCallback)

      • getGroupByGroupName

        @Deprecated
void getGroupByGroupName(java.lang.String groupName,
                                     MASCallback<java.util.List<MASGroup>> callback)
        Deprecated. Please use getGroupsByFilter(MASFilteredRequest, MASCallback)

        Retrieves all MASGroup objects that match the specified group name.

        WARNING: this is not an 'equalTo' match on the groupName, rather it is a 'contains' match.
        Parameters:
        groupName - The group name to be used in the search.
        callback - Callback with either the list of MASGroup or an error.
